<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0">
    <teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>The Political Adviser in Siam (
                        Yost
                    ) to the Secretary of
                            State</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1945v06</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d1036</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">1036</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1945-12-25T01:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1945-12-25T01:00:00-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-12-25T01:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-12-25T01:00:00-05:00" n="1036" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1036">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">741.92/12–2545: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Political Adviser in Siam</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Yost</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bangkok</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-12-25T13:00:00+07:00">December 25, 1945—1 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 10:18 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>96. Reurtel 80, December 22, 4 p.m. Believe January 1 would be wholly suitable
                    day. Formal agreement may not be concluded until <pb facs="1422" n="1410" xml:id="pg_1410"/> some time in January but it would seem quite proper for
                    us to act after Heads of Agreement have been signed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Yost</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
